paragraph_english: The American Embassy in Nepal has organized Creators Mela-2026 with the aim of connecting digital creation with creative and economic income among the common people.   The Creators Fair, which started from Chitwan with the slogan 'Vision to Venture', has been conducted in Kathmandu since Friday. After the active operation of Chitwan and Nepalgunj, the embassy has organized two days in Kathmandu till Saturday to enjoy digital creation in Kathmandu, according to the embassy.
